  "action": "type_string",
  "text": "; Draw a picture once, grab it as a shape, then stamp it everywhere.\nBLITZ\n  ; draw a target on a small work bitmap, then grab it as shape 0\n  BitMap 1,32,32,3\n  For i=1 To 14\n    Circle 16,16,i,2+i/5\n  Next\n  GetaShape 0,0,0,32,32\n\n  ; the display bitmap\n  BitMap 0,320,256,3\n  Cls 0\n  For n=0 To 8\n    Blit 0,n*34+8,112\n  Next\n\n  VWait 100\n  Slice 0,44,3\n  Show 0\n  MouseWait\n"
 },
